quran[49]{c,v,t}:
  15,1,Alif Lam Ra lawa ngamavesi encwadi neQur’an ecacile
  15,2,"Mhlawumbe\tlabo\tabangakholwanga\tbayofisa\tsengathi babezinikele ngaphansi kwentando kaMvelinqangi"
  15,3,"Bayeke bazidlele, bazijabulise futhi babanjezelwe ithemba (elingeyilutho) ngakho-ke bazokwazi"
  15,4,Futhi asizange silibhubhise idolobha ngaphandle kokuba kwakuyisimemezelo salo esaziwayo
  15,5,Asikho isizwe esingajahisa phambili isikhathi saso noma sisilibazise
  15,6,"Futhi bathi, “Oh wena! Okwembulwe kuye isikhumbuzo (iQur’an) ngempela wena uyahlanya”"
  15,7,"Kungani\tungezi\tkuthina\tnezingelosi\tuma\tkungukuthi ungomunye wabaneqiniso na"
  15,8,"Asizithumeli\tizingelosi\tphansi\tngaphandle\tuma\t(ziza) nesijeziso futhi (abangakholwayo) angeke banikwe ithuba"
  15,9,Ngempela thina sasembula isikhumbuzo (iQur’an) futhi ngempela thina singabalondolozi baso
  15,10,"Futhi\tngempela\tsathumela\t(izithunywa)\tngaphambilini kwakho (Oh Muhammad!) phakathi kwabantu basendulo"
  15,11,Futhi sasingafiki kubona isithunywa ngaphandle kokuba basenze inhlekisa
  15,12,Sikwenze kanjalo ukuba kungene ezinhliziyweni zezoni
  15,13,Abakholelwa kuyona (iQur’an) futhi ngempela sesadlula isibonelo salabo basendulo
  15,14,"Futhi\tnoma\tngabe\tsabavulela\tumnyango\twezulu babezoqhubeka bakhuphuke lapho"
  15,15,"Babezothi, “kuphela amehlo ethu abexhoshiwe kepha thina singabantu abalunjiwe.”"
  15,16,Futhi ngempela sabeka izinkanyezi ezinkulu ezulwini futhi sazenza zabukeka zizinhle kwabazibonayo
  15,17,Futhi saliqaphela kubona bonke osathane abagxoshiwe (embusweni kaMvelinqangi)
  15,18,Ngaphandle kwalowo (sathane) ontshontsha ukulalela ngakho-ke ulandelwa ilangabi eligqamile
  15,19,Nomhlaba sawendlala senza kuwona izintaba ezisimeme futhi senza ukuthi kumile kuwona zonke izinto ngendlela efanele
  15,20,Futhi sanenzela kuwona izindlela zokuphila kanye nalezo (zidalwa) eningazondli (izinkomo nokunye)
  15,21,Futhi akukho lutho olungekho kepha kuthina kunokugcinwa kwako futhi angeke sikwehlisele phansi ngaphandle ngesilinganiso esaziwayo
  15,22,Futhi sathumela imimoya ukuze ivundise sabe sesinethisa imvula evela esibhakabhakeni ukuze siniphuzise yona futhi nina aniyibona abagcini bayo (imvula)
  15,23,Futhi ngempela thina siyaphilisa futhi siyabulala futhi siyizindlalifa
  15,24,Futhi ngempela siyabazi abeza kuqala kunani (izizukulwane ezafika ngaphambilini kwenu) futhi ngempela siyabazi abayoza emveni (kwalokho)
  15,25,"Futhi ngempela iNkosi yakho iyobaqoqela ndawonye, ngempela yona inobuhlakani iyazi"
  15,26,Futhi ngempela samdala umuntu ngobumba olomile olubhucukile oluqhamuka emhlabathini ecwelekile
  15,27,NamaJinn sawadala ngaphambilini ngamalangabi omlilo
  15,28,Futhi (khumbula) ngenkathi iNkosi yakho ithi ezingelosini ngempela mina ngingumdali womuntu ngobumba olomileyo ocubuzekile oluqhamuka emhlabathini ocwelekileyo
  15,29,Ngakho-ke kwathi lapho sengimenzile (u-Adam) ngaphefumulela umoya wami kuyena ngakho-ke ngathi yiwani nimkhothamele
  15,30,Ngakho-ke izingelosi zamkhothamela zonke
  15,31,Ngaphandle kuka-Iblis wenqaba ukuthi abe kanye nabakhothamayo
  15,32,"(UMvelinqangi) wathi, “Oh Iblis! kwenzenjani ngawe ukuthi ungabi kanye nabakhothamayo na?”"
  15,33,Wathi (u-Iblis) “angeke ngikwazi ukukhothamela umuntu owamdala ngobumba olucubuzekileyo oluphuma emhlabathini ocwelekileyo”
  15,34,Wathi (uMvelinqangi) phuma kulona (izulu) ngakho-ke ngempela wena ungogxoshiweyo (embusweni wezulu)
  15,35,Futhi ngempela phezu kwakho kunesiqalekiso kuze kube ilanga lokuvuka kwabafileyo.”
  15,36,"(U-Iblis) wathi, “Nkosi yami nginike ithuba kuze kube usuku lokuvuswa kwabafileyo”"
  15,37,Wathi (uMvelinqangi) ngempela wena ungomunye wabanikwe ithuba
  15,38,Kuze kube usuku lwesikhathi esiqokiwe
  15,39,"(U-Iblis) wathi, “Nkosi yami ngokuba ungidukisile ngempela ngizokwenza (ukona) kubukeke kukuhle kubona (abantu) emhlabeni futhi ngempela ngizobadukisa bonke.”"
  15,40,Ngaphandle kwezinceku zakho (eziholiwe) phakathi kwabo
  15,41,Wathi “lena indlela yami eqondile (elungileyo).”
  15,42,Ngempela ezincekwini zami awunagunya phezu kwazo ngaphandle kwalezo ezikulandelayo ezidukileyo
  15,43,Futhi ngempela isihogo siyisithembiso sabo bonke (labo abalandela u-Iblis)
  15,44,Sinamasango ayisikhombisa isango nesango lalawomasango kunengxenye (yezoni) ebekiwe (kulona)
  15,45,"Ngempela\tabenza\tokulungileyo\tbayohlala\tezivandeni nasemithonjeni yamanzi"
  15,46,"(Kuyothiwa kubona), “Ngenani kusona (isivande) ngokuthula niphephile”"
  15,47,Futhi siyosusa konke okusezifubeni zabo okubi okuyinzondo bahlale njengabazalwane ezihlalweni eziqhwakele ezibhekene
  15,48,Angeke kubathinte ukukhathazeka khona lapho (esivandeni) futhi bona angeke bakhishwe kusona
  15,49,"Zitshele\tizinceku\tzami\tukuthi\tmina\tngiyathethelela nginesihawu"